│ The proposed fix ensures that the `generatePerPart` function │
│ respects the `GeneratesPerFirstLaneOnly` flag by extracting  │
│ the first lane of the vector when necessary. This resolves   │
│ the mismatch between the `GeneratedValue` type and the       │
│ expected type, preventing the assertion failure. The fix is  │
│ localized and does not affect other parts of the code, as it │
│ only modifies the behavior of `generatePerPart` when         │
│ `GeneratesPerFirstLaneOnly` is `true`.                       │
